**Summary:**
This Japanese documentation explains how to build funnel analysis charts in Amplitude, covering event ordering options (any order, this order, exact order), user segmentation, event exclusion, optional steps, and advanced features like inline event combinations and multi-event comparisons within single funnel steps.

